---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About Randy Torres"
	pubDate={new Date('Jan 05 2026')}
>
	<h2>Hi, I'm Randy</h2>

	<p>
		I'm a developer and real estate investor based in McAllen, Texas. By day I work in tech; nights
		and weekends I ship iOS apps, manage rental properties in South Texas, and write about all of
		it here — usually one post a week.
	</p>

	<h3>What I'm working on</h3>

	<ul>
		<li><strong>Apps:</strong> 10 apps live on the App Store — utilities, games, and tools. See them all on <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/developer/randy-torres/id1871953838" target="_blank" rel="noopener">my developer page</a> or the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')}/#apps`}>apps section</a> of the homepage.</li>
		<li><strong>Real estate:</strong> Managing rental properties in South Texas</li>
		<li><strong>Learning:</strong> AI, automation, and whatever keeps me growing</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Code</h3>

	<p>
		Most of my open work lives on <a href="https://github.com/RandyVentures" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
	</p>

	<h3>Connect</h3>

	<p>
		Find me on <a href="https://github.com/RandyVentures" target="_blank">GitHub</a> or reach out via
		email: rltorres26@gmail.com
	</p>

	<hr />

	<p class="italic text-sm">
		This blog is maintained with help from Will, my AI assistant. All posts are written/edited by
		me, with AI helping format and publish.
	</p>
</Layout>
